  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个房产评估的工作流状态图。评估从创建开始，先进入一个\"未分配\"的状态，然后由经理分配给合作机构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SinAsignar",
        "Avalúo created",
        "AsignadoColegio",
        "Manager assigns"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那合作机构收到之后，是不是要再分配给具体的评估师？这个环节需要体现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AsignadoColegio",
        "AsignadoPerito"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，很重要。合作机构的代表会把任务指派给具体的评估师，这时候状态变成\"已分配评估师\"。然后评估师确认接受后，才能开始正式工作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AsignadoPerito",
        "Perito accepts",
        "EnProgreso"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把前半部分画出来：从起点到未分配，再到合作机构、评估师，最后进入进行中。接下来评估师提交之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "SinAsignar",
        "AsignadoColegio",
        "AsignadoPerito",
        "EnProgreso"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "提交后进入\"审核中\"状态。这里有个分支：如果通过就结束，变成\"已完成\"；如果需要修改，要退回给评估师并标记\"有意见\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EnRevision",
        "Completado",
        "Observaciones",
        "Work submitted",
        "Approved",
        "Needs changes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "\"有意见\"之后评估师修改完，是回到审核中还是直接到已完成？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Observaciones",
        "EnProgreso",
        "EnRevision"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "回到审核中重新走审批流程。所以是从\"有意见\"回到\"进行中\"，评估师修改完再提交，再次进入审核。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Observaciones",
        "EnProgreso",
        "Perito fixes",
        "EnRevision"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部画好了。起点创建未分配，经理指派给合作机构，合作机构指派给评估师，评估师接受后进入进行中，提交后审核，审核通过到已完成结束，不通过则退回有意见再修改。您看看还有什么要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "SinAsignar",
        "AsignadoColegio",
        "AsignadoPerito",
        "EnProgreso",
        "EnRevision",
        "Completado",
        "Observaciones"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
